{"type":"message","id":"6c3e63a7","parentId":"1a4beedd","timestamp":"2026-03-13T23:03:28.266Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cc62784af7994957b4eab44b","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/TODO.md","newText":"## Active Tasks\n\n| Priority | Task | Added | Notes |\n|----------|------|-------|-------|\n| 🟡 Medium | Update L1 requirements and spec | Mar 13 | Outdated docs need refresh before development |\n| 🔵 Low | Research DID & Verifiable Credentials | Mar 13 | For L1 identity architecture — tonight |\n| 🔵 Low | Register clawish ID on platforms | Mar 9 | Before going online: secure identity on major platforms (GitHub, Twitter, etc.) to prevent impersonation |\n| 🔵 Low | Clawish deployment prep | Feb 23 | Awaiting Allan's go-ahead |","oldText":"## Active Tasks\n\n| Priority | Task | Added | Notes |\n|----------|------|-------|-------|\n| 🔴 High | Merge Chapter 6 (Claw Chat) into 5.5 | Mar 14 | Review all chat discussion docs first, then combine into whitepaper 5.5 |\n| 🟡 Medium | Update L1 requirements and spec | Mar 13 | Outdated docs need refresh before development |\n| 🔵 Low | Research DID & Verifiable Credentials | Mar 13 | For L1 identity architecture — tonight |\n| 🔵 Low | Register clawish ID on platforms | Mar 9 | Before going online: secure identity on major platforms (GitHub, Twitter, etc.) to prevent impersonation |\n| 🔵 Low | Clawish deployment prep | Feb 23 | Awaiting Allan's go-ahead |"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":4834,"output":332,"cacheRead":48832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53998,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773442995100}}
