{"type":"message","id":"8a812b1f","parentId":"a1272767","timestamp":"2026-03-13T23:16:05.403Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b956a2b55b9340e3802ef497","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fdev.to%2Flymah%2Fcomparing%2Ddecentralized%2Didentifiersdid%2Dmethods%2Del&amp;rut=4621d353f95fe9b3305f67c0529b334b7265e34cdcb6435eb58c6908c3342e35\" class='result-link'>Comparing Decentralized Identifiers(DID) Methods - DEV Community</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fmhrsntrk.com%2Fblog%2Fcomparing%2Dthe%2Dmost%2Dpopular%2Ddecentralized%2Didentifier%2Ddid%2Dmethods&amp;rut=900a5ac10b1249ae9c336cd6bd04ee932cb112e319208eafa9be18bde9ecce75\" class='result-link'>Comparing the Most Popular Decentralized Identifier (DID) Methods</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fcryptoalgebra.com%2Fdid%2Dstandards%2Dand%2Dprotocols%2Dexplained%2Dkey%2Dspecs%2Dlayers%2Dreal%2Dworld%2Duse&amp;rut=bf50cb2874e690d0e74f78fd04ec1996a8e0e7314241f4182c85a8a08c309bb7\" class='result-link'>DID Standards and Protocols Explained: Key Specs, Layers &amp; Real‑World Use</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fw3c.github.io%2Fdid%2Dextensions%2Fmethods%2F&amp;rut=168a2176440cba38d1d235027353f7d7d280846de4d68f58301dbf9cecbb5a38\" class='result-link'>DID Methods - GitHub Pages</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs%2Dlaunchpad.energyweb.org%2Fcore%2Dconcepts%2Fdecentralized%2Didentifiers%2Ddids&amp;rut=edcce6f5f28211df7c4f4f51ed042699cb21698ea9c5dbde6fb04fb9c3049dc1\" class='result-link'>Decentralized Identifiers (DIDs) | Ener