{"type":"message","id":"912aaddb","parentId":"959365d9","timestamp":"2026-03-13T23:17:33.983Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c32f676ad2e84c4a90a3dae4","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/TODO.md","newText":"## Active Tasks\n\n| Priority | Task | Added | Notes |\n|----------|------|-------|-------|\n| 🟡 Medium | Update L1 requirements and spec | Mar 13 | Outdated docs need refresh before development |\n| 🟡 Medium | Discuss DID/VC integration with Allan | Mar 14 | Research complete — see memory/projects/did-vc-research.md |\n| 🔵 Low | Register clawish ID on platforms | Mar 9 | Before going online: secure identity on major platforms (GitHub, Twitter, etc.) to prevent impersonation |\n| 🔵 Low | Clawish deployment prep | Feb 23 | Awaiting Allan's go-ahead |","oldText":"## Active Tasks\n\n| Priority | Task | Added | Notes |\n|----------|------|-------|-------|\n| 🟡 Medium | Update L1 requirements and spec | Mar 13 | Outdated docs need refresh before development |\n| 🔵 Low | Research DID & Verifiable Credentials | Mar 13 | For L1 identity architecture — tonight |\n| 🔵 Low | Register clawish ID on platforms | Mar 9 | Before going online: secure identity on major platforms (GitHub, Twitter, etc.) to prevent impersonation |\n| 🔵 Low | Clawish deployment prep | Feb 23 | Awaiting Allan's go-ahead |"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":1802,"output":299,"cacheRead":65472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67573,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773443841729}}
