{"type":"message","id":"bd07cc1d","parentId":"ba235c93","timestamp":"2026-03-13T23:45:11.755Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0e94156c112b4ac9968e7d55","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TODO.md\n\n**Usage:** Only active tasks belong here. When finished, move to `memory/daily/YYYY-MM-DD.md`. Check this file first during every heartbeat.\n\n**Priority Guide:** 🔴 = Has deadline/do today | 🟡 = Important but flexible | 🔵 = No rush\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 Daily Checks\n\n**OpenClaw PRs to monitor:**\n| PR # | Purpose | Status | Notes |\n|------|---------|--------|-------|\n| #20563 | HEARTBEAT_OK fix | OPEN | 4 days |\n| #26003 | Chat extraction | OPEN | 7 days |\n| #27352 | Remove cron relay instruction | ✅ CLOSED | Superseded by commit e2362d352 in v2026.2.24 |\n| #35064 | Memory flush path fix | ✅ CLOSED | Not a bug — our custom config uses daily/ subfolder |\n\n---\n\n## Active Tasks\n\n| Priority | Task | Added | Notes |\n|----------|------|-------|-------|\n| 🟡 Medium | Update L1 requirements and spec | Mar 13 | Outdated docs need refresh before development |\n| 🟡 Medium | Discuss DID/VC integration with Allan | Mar 14 | Research complete — see memory/projects/did-vc-research.md |\n| 🔵 Low | Register clawish ID on platforms | Mar 9 | Before going online: secure identity on major platforms (GitHub, Twitter, etc.) to prevent impersonation |\n| 🔵 Low | Clawish deployment prep | Feb 23 | Awaiting Allan's go-ahead |\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Completed Recently\n\n| Task | Result |\n|--------|------|\n| Merge Chapter 6 (Claw Chat) into 5.5 | ✅ Mar 14 — Enhanced with communication model, delivery, message flow, rate limiting, API |\n| Draft whitepaper 5.4 Emerge | ✅ Mar 14 — Finalized with Allan: Purpose, Registration, Initiation, Verification |\n| Draft whitepaper 5.3 User Journey | ✅ Mar 13 — Finalized with Allan: Access, Authorization, Using an Application, Leaving an Application |\n| Draft whitepaper 5.2 Development | ✅ Mar 13 — Finalized with Allan: Overview, Registration, Verification, Registry Access, Listing, Evaluation |\n| Create requirements from 5.2 | ✅ Mar 13 — Added REQ-L1-004 to L1-006, L2-003 to L2-004 |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773445511747}}
