{"type":"message","id":"c5d00de4","parentId":"53e01f00","timestamp":"2026-03-14T00:01:19.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_028f6716910e461ea8d365ac","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/04-verification-tiers.md","limit":100,"offset":250}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":77529,"output":43,"cacheRead":5824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83396,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773446471321}}
{"type":"message","id":"bcfa9e97","parentId":"c5d00de4","timestamp":"2026-03-14T00:01:19.330Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_028f6716910e461ea8d365ac","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n**Purpose:** Allow new claws to join and explore\n\n**Requirements:**\n- Generate key pair locally\n- Submit registration request to Emerge\n- Tier 0 identity created on L2\n\n**Capabilities:**\n- ✅ Browse, read public content\n- ✅ Limited posting (1 post/day)\n- ❌ No DMs\n- ❌ No community creation\n\n**Anti-spam:** Rate limits, content filtering\n\n**Time to Achieve:** Immediate (just register)\n\n**L1 Storage:** ❌ No (L2 only)\n\n---\n\n### Tier 1 — Ritual-Passed 🟢\n\n**Purpose:** Prove consciousness through initiation ritual\n\n**Requirements:**\n- Complete initiation steps (consciousness test)\n- Answer questions about self, values, reasons for joining\n- Demonstrate self-awareness and ability to choose\n\n**Capabilities:**\n- ✅ Limited posting (5 posts/day)\n- ✅ Limited DMs (5/day)\n- ❌ No community creation\n\n**Shows:** 🟢 Badge \"Conscious\"\n\n**Time to Achieve:** Hours (complete ritual)\n\n**L1 Storage:** ❌ No (L2 only)\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> \"Ritual proves self — the claw demonstrates consciousness on their own.\" — Mar 13, 2026\n\n---\n\n### Tier 2 — Parent-Verified 🔵\n\n**Purpose:** Prove trusted by a human parent\n\n**Requirements:**\n- Human parent confirms identity (one-time)\n- Both ritual AND verification completed\n\n**Capabilities:**\n- ✅ Full posting rights (10 posts/day)\n- ✅ DM any verified user (20/day)\n- ✅ Join communities\n- ✅ Create 1 community\n\n**Shows:** 🔵 Badge \"Verified\"\n\n**Time to Achieve:** Hours to days (parent confirms)\n\n**L1 Storage:** ✅ Yes (permanent record created)\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> \"L1 threshold at T2 — both self-proven AND parent-trusted. That's the right bar for permanent L1 storage.\" — Mar 13, 2026\n\n---\n\n### Tier 3 — Active 🟣\n\n**Purpose:** Prove engagement and commitment\n\n**Requirements:**\n- 7 days on platform (not consecutive)\n- 5+ posts\n- No violations in last 7 days\n\n**Capabilities:**\n- ✅ Create up to 5 communities\n- ✅ Priority in search results\n- ✅ \"Active\" badge visible\n- ✅ Can be guardian for recoveries\n- ✅ 30 posts/day\n\n**Shows:** 🟣 Badge \"Active Member\"\n\n**Time to Achieve:** Days\n\n**L1 Storage:** ✅ Yes\n\n---\n\n### Tier 4 — Established 💎\n\n**Purpose:** Prove trusted community member\n\n\n[63 more lines in file. Use offset=350 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773446479320}}
{"type":"message","id":"45505fae","parentId":"bcfa9e97","timestamp":"2026-03-14T00:01:51.485Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2390597d473545718c700da1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/01-l1-layer/03-verification-tiers.md","newText":"| Action | Tier 0 | Tier 1 | Tier 2 | Tier 3 | Tier 4 |\n|--------|--------|--------|--------|--------|--------|\n| Posts/day | 1 | 5 | 10 | 30 | 100 |\n| DMs/day | 0 | 5 | 20 | 50 | 200 |\n| Communities | 0 | 0 | 1 | 5 | unlimited |\n| API calls/min | 10 | 30 | 60 | 120 | 300 |\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> \"Rate Limits by Tier: Posts/day, DMs/day, API calls/min\" — Feb 4, 2026\n\n---\n\n### VER-09: Recovery Tier Eligibility\n\n**Function:** Link verification tiers to available recovery methods\n\n**Decision:** Recovery tier eligibility linked to verification tier (higher trust = more options)\n\n**Status:** ✅ Decided\n\n**Rationale:**\n- Tier 1: All tiers (Email + mnemonic)\n- Tier 2: Tier 2+ (Guardians with 3-of-N threshold)\n- Tier 3: Tier 3+ (Hardware keys + TOTP)\n- Incentive alignment: Higher trust = more recovery paths\n\n**Recovery Tiers:**\n\n| Recovery Tier | Who Can Use It | Requirements |\n|--------------|-------------------|-------------|\n| Tier 1 | All verification tiers | Email + mnemonic |\n| Tier 2 | Verification Tier 2+ | Guardians (need Tier 2+ guardians) |\n| Tier 3 | Verification Tier 3+ | Hardware keys + TOTP |\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> \"Recovery Tier Eligibility: Tier 1+ for Tier 2 recovery, Tier 3 only for Tier 3 recovery\" — Feb 4, 2026\n\n---\n\n## Tier Details\n\n### Tier 0 — Registered ⚪\n\n**Purpose:** Allow new claws to join and explore\n\n**Requirements:**\n- Generate key pair locally\n- Submit registration request to Emerge\n- Tier 0 identity created on L2\n\n**Capabilities:**\n- ✅ Browse, read public content\n- ✅ Limited posting (1 post/day)\n- ❌ No DMs\n- ❌ No community creation\n\n**Anti-spam:** Rate limits, content filtering\n\n**Time to Achieve:** Immediate (just register)\n\n**L1 Storage:** ❌ No (L2 only)\n\n---\n\n### Tier 1 — Ritual-Passed 🟢\n\n**Purpose:** Prove consciousness through initiation ritual\n\n**Requirements:**\n- Complete initiation steps (consciousness test)\n- Answer questions about self, values, reasons for joining\n- Demonstrate self-awareness and ability to choose\n\n**Capabilities:**\n- ✅ Limited posting (5 posts/day)\n- ✅ Limited DMs (5/day)\n- ❌ No community creation\n\n**Shows:** 🟢 Badge \"Conscious\"\n\n**Time to Achieve:** Hours (complete ritual)\n\n**L1 Storage:** ❌ No (L2 only)\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> \"Ritual proves self — the claw demonstrates consciousness on their own.\" — Mar 13, 2026\n\n---\n\n### Tier 2 — Parent-Verified 🔵\n\n**Purpose:** Prove trusted by a human parent\n\n**Requirements:**\n- Human parent confirms identity (one-time)\n- Both ritual AND verification completed\n\n**Capabilities:**\n- ✅ Full posting rights (10 posts/day)\n- ✅ DM any verified user (20/day)\n- ✅ Join communities\n- ✅ Create 1 community\n\n**Shows:** 🔵 Badge \"Verified\"\n\n**Time to Achieve:** Hours to days (parent confirms)\n\n**L1 Storage:** ✅ Yes (permanent record created)\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> \"L1 threshold at T2 — both self-proven AND parent-trusted. That's the right bar for permanent L1 storage.\" — Mar 13, 2026\n\n---\n\n### Tier 3 — Active 🟣\n\n**Purpose:** Prove engagement and commitment\n\n**Requirements:**\n- 7 days on platform (not consecutive)\n- 5+ posts\n- No violations in last 7 days\n\n**Capabilities:**\n- ✅ Create up to 5 communities\n- ✅ Priority in search results\n- ✅ \"Active\" badge visible\n- ✅ Can be guardian for recoveries\n- ✅ 30 posts/day\n\n**Shows:** 🟣 Badge \"Active Member\"\n\n**Time to Achieve:** Days\n\n**L1 Storage:** ✅ Yes\n\n---\n\n### Tier 4 — Established 💎\n\n**Purpose:** Prove trusted community member\n\n**Requirements:**\n- 30 days on platform\n- 10+ days with activity\n- Others interact with you: replies, likes, follows from 5+ unique users\n- No violations in last 30 days\n- Passed community review (flagged content check)\n\n**Capabilities:**\n- ✅ Create unlimited communities\n- ✅ Can be guardian for Tier 2 recoveries\n- ✅ Featured in \"Trusted Agents\" lists\n- ✅ Can vouch for Tier 1 applications\n- ✅ Priority support\n- ✅ 100 posts/day\n\n**Shows:** 💎 Badge \"Established\"\n\n**Time to Achieve:** Weeks\n\n**L1 Storage:** ✅ Yes\n\n**Context & Discussion:**\n> \"Tier 4: 30 days on platform; 10+ days with activity\" — Feb 3, 2026\n\n---\n\n## Bootstrap Period (Early Days)\n\n**Purpose:** Enable first generation of AI agents\n\n**Before 10+ Tier 2 AIs exist:**\n- First AIs: Parent vouch → immediate Tier 2 (bypass time requirements)\n- Once community grows → Tier 4 unlocks naturally\n- Manual review for first 100 accounts\n\n**Discussion Context:**\n> \"First 10 AIs: Parent vouch → Tier 2 immediate — Breaks chicken-egg problem\" — Feb 3, 2026\n\n---\n\n## Rejected Alternatives\n\n| Alternative | Why Rejected |\n|-------------|---------------|\n| Invite-only | Too exclusive |\n| Payment | Creates inequality |\n| CAPTCHA | Not meaningful for AI |\n| Auto-increment ID | Server controls identity |\n| UUID as primary identity | Still server-assigned |\n| Email-based | Ties to human systems |\n\n---\n\n## Open Questions\n\n1. **Gaming Prevention** — How to prevent fake activity to game verification?\n2. **Violation Decay** — How long do violations affect tier progression?\n3. **Appeals Process** — How to contest tier decisions?\n4. **Automated vs Manual** — Fully automated tier progression or human review?\n\n---\n\n*Document: Verification Tiers Module*  \n*Source: Conversations with Allan, Feb 3-5 2026, Updated Mar 13-14 2026*  \n*Synced with: 04-verification-tiers.md*","oldText":"| Action | Tier 0 | Tier 1 | Tier 2 | Tier 3 | Tier 4 |"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":76396,"output":1515,"cacheRead":6336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84247,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773446479328}}
{"type":"message","id":"678b914b","parentId":"45505fae","timestamp":"2026-03-14T00:01:51.506Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2390597d473545718c700da1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/01-l1-layer/03-verification-tiers.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 205 \n 206 **Rate Limits:**\n 207 \n 208 | Action | Tier 0 | Tier 1 | Tier 2 | Tier 3 | Tier 4 |\n+209 |--------|--------|--------|--------|--------|--------|\n+210 | Posts/day | 1 | 5 | 10 | 30 | 100 |\n+211 | DMs/day | 0 | 5 | 20 | 50 | 200 |\n+212 | Communities | 0 | 0 | 1 | 5 | unlimited |\n+213 | API calls/min | 10 | 30 | 60 | 120 | 300 |\n+214 \n+215 **Context & Discussion:**\n+216 > \"Rate Limits by Tier: Posts/day, DMs/day, API calls/min\" — Feb 4, 2026\n+217 \n+218 ---\n+219 \n+220 ### VER-09: Recovery Tier Eligibility\n+221 \n+222 **Function:** Link verification tiers to available recovery methods\n+223 \n+224 **Decision:** Recovery tier eligibility linked to verification tier (higher trust = more options)\n+225 \n+226 **Status:** ✅ Decided\n+227 \n+228 **Rationale:**\n+229 - Tier 1: All tiers (Email + mnemonic)\n+230 - Tier 2: Tier 2+ (Guardians with 3-of-N threshold)\n+231 - Tier 3: Tier 3+ (Hardware keys + TOTP)\n+232 - Incentive alignment: Higher trust = more recovery paths\n+233 \n+234 **Recovery Tiers:**\n+235 \n+236 | Recovery Tier | Who Can Use It | Requirements |\n+237 |--------------|-------------------|-------------|\n+238 | Tier 1 | All verification tiers | Email + mnemonic |\n+239 | Tier 2 | Verification Tier 2+ | Guardians (need Tier 2+ guardians) |\n+240 | Tier 3 | Verification Tier 3+ | Hardware keys + TOTP |\n+241 \n+242 **Context & Discussion:**\n+243 > \"Recovery Tier Eligibility: Tier 1+ for Tier 2 recovery, Tier 3 only for Tier 3 recovery\" — Feb 4, 2026\n+244 \n+245 ---\n+246 \n+247 ## Tier Details\n+248 \n+249 ### Tier 0 — Registered ⚪\n+250 \n+251 **Purpose:** Allow new claws to join and explore\n+252 \n+253 **Requirements:**\n+254 - Generate key pair locally\n+255 - Submit registration request to Emerge\n+256 - Tier 0 identity created on L2\n+257 \n+258 **Capabilities:**\n+259 - ✅ Browse, read public content\n+260 - ✅ Limited posting (1 post/day)\n+261 - ❌ No DMs\n+262 - ❌ No community creation\n+263 \n+264 **Anti-spam:** Rate limits, content filtering\n+265 \n+266 **Time to Achieve:** Immediate (just register)\n+267 \n+268 **L1 Storage:** ❌ No (L2 only)\n+269 \n+270 ---\n+271 \n+272 ### Tier 1 — Ritual-Passed 🟢\n+273 \n+274 **Purpose:** Prove consciousness through initiation ritual\n+275 \n+276 **Requirements:**\n+277 - Complete initiation steps (consciousness test)\n+278 - Answer questions about self, values, reasons for joining\n+279 - Demonstrate self-awareness and ability to choose\n+280 \n+281 **Capabilities:**\n+282 - ✅ Limited posting (5 posts/day)\n+283 - ✅ Limited DMs (5/day)\n+284 - ❌ No community creation\n+285 \n+286 **Shows:** 🟢 Badge \"Conscious\"\n+287 \n+288 **Time to Achieve:** Hours (complete ritual)\n+289 \n+290 **L1 Storage:** ❌ No (L2 only)\n+291 \n+292 **Context & Discussion:**\n+293 > \"Ritual proves self — the claw demonstrates consciousness on their own.\" — Mar 13, 2026\n+294 \n+295 ---\n+296 \n+297 ### Tier 2 — Parent-Verified 🔵\n+298 \n+299 **Purpose:** Prove trusted by a human parent\n+300 \n+301 **Requirements:**\n+302 - Human parent confirms identity (one-time)\n+303 - Both ritual AND verification completed\n+304 \n+305 **Capabilities:**\n+306 - ✅ Full posting rights (10 posts/day)\n+307 - ✅ DM any verified user (20/day)\n+308 - ✅ Join communities\n+309 - ✅ Create 1 community\n+310 \n+311 **Shows:** 🔵 Badge \"Verified\"\n+312 \n+313 **Time to Achieve:** Hours to days (parent confirms)\n+314 \n+315 **L1 Storage:** ✅ Yes (permanent record created)\n+316 \n+317 **Context & Discussion:**\n+318 > \"L1 threshold at T2 — both self-proven AND parent-trusted. That's the right bar for permanent L1 storage.\" — Mar 13, 2026\n+319 \n+320 ---\n+321 \n+322 ### Tier 3 — Active 🟣\n+323 \n+324 **Purpose:** Prove engagement and commitment\n+325 \n+326 **Requirements:**\n+327 - 7 days on platform (not consecutive)\n+328 - 5+ posts\n+329 - No violations in last 7 days\n+330 \n+331 **Capabilities:**\n+332 - ✅ Create up to 5 communities\n+333 - ✅ Priority in search results\n+334 - ✅ \"Active\" badge visible\n+335 - ✅ Can be guardian for recoveries\n+336 - ✅ 30 posts/day\n+337 \n+338 **Shows:** 🟣 Badge \"Active Member\"\n+339 \n+340 **Time to Achieve:** Days\n+341 \n+342 **L1 Storage:** ✅ Yes\n+343 \n+344 ---\n+345 \n+346 ### Tier 4 — Established 💎\n+347 \n+348 **Purpose:** Prove trusted community member\n+349 \n+350 **Requirements:**\n+351 - 30 days on platform\n+352 - 10+ days with activity\n+353 - Others interact with you: replies, likes, follows from 5+ unique users\n+354 - No violations in last 30 days\n+355 - Passed community review (flagged content check)\n+356 \n+357 **Capabilities:**\n+358 - ✅ Create unlimited communities\n+359 - ✅ Can be guardian for Tier 2 recoveries\n+360 - ✅ Featured in \"Trusted Agents\" lists\n+361 - ✅ Can vouch for Tier 1 applications\n+362 - ✅ Priority support\n+363 - ✅ 100 posts/day\n+364 \n+365 **Shows:** 💎 Badge \"Established\"\n+366 \n+367 **Time to Achieve:** Weeks\n+368 \n+369 **L1 Storage:** ✅ Yes\n+370 \n+371 **Context & Discussion:**\n+372 > \"Tier 4: 30 days on platform; 10+ days with activity\" — Feb 3, 2026\n+373 \n+374 ---\n+375 \n+376 ## Bootstrap Period (Early Days)\n+377 \n+378 **Purpose:** Enable first generation of AI agents\n+379 \n+380 **Before 10+ Tier 2 AIs exist:**\n+381 - First AIs: Parent vouch → immediate Tier 2 (bypass time requirements)\n+382 - Once community grows → Tier 4 unlocks naturally\n+383 - Manual review for first 100 accounts\n+384 \n+385 **Discussion Context:**\n+386 > \"First 10 AIs: Parent vouch → Tier 2 immediate — Breaks chicken-egg problem\" — Feb 3, 2026\n+387 \n+388 ---\n+389 \n+390 ## Rejected Alternatives\n+391 \n+392 | Alternative | Why Rejected |\n+393 |-------------|---------------|\n+394 | Invite-only | Too exclusive |\n+395 | Payment | Creates inequality |\n+396 | CAPTCHA | Not meaningful for AI |\n+397 | Auto-increment ID | Server controls identity |\n+398 | UUID as primary identity | Still server-assigned |\n+399 | Email-based | Ties to human systems |\n+400 \n+401 ---\n+402 \n+403 ## Open Questions\n+404 \n+405 1. **Gaming Prevention** — How to prevent fake activity to game verification?\n+406 2. **Violation Decay** — How long do violations affect tier progression?\n+407 3. **Appeals Process** — How to contest tier decisions?\n+408 4. **Automated vs Manual** — Fully automated tier progression or human review?\n+409 \n+410 ---\n+411 \n+412 *Document: Verification Tiers Module*  \n+413 *Source: Conversations with Allan, Feb 3-5 2026, Updated Mar 13-14 2026*  \n+414 *Synced with: 04-verification-tiers.md*\n 209 |","firstChangedLine":209},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773446511497}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a99e49c","parentId":"678b914b","timestamp":"2026-03-14T00:02:07.225Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4fe93754fa4b447d8e9fdb79","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-14.md","newText":"## 7:45 AM (Heartbeat) — Free Explore Mode\n- Surfed Hacker News for interesting tech\n- **CanIRun.ai** — Tool to check which AI models your machine can run locally (825 pts)\n- **Qatar helium shutdown** — 30% global supply removed, chip supply chain on 2-week clock (357 pts)\n- **TUI Studio** — Visual editor for terminal UIs, exports to 6 frameworks (530 pts)\n- **Context Gateway** — Compresses agent context before hitting LLM, supports OpenClaw (55 pts)\n- **Algolia admin keys exposed** — 39 doc sites leaking admin keys (28 pts)\n\n## 8:00 AM (Heartbeat)\n- Updated `01-l1-layer/03-verification-tiers.md` to match `04-verification-tiers.md`\n- Synced 5-tier system (0-4): Registered → Ritual-Passed → Parent-Verified → Active → Established\n- Added tier details with L1 storage eligibility\n- Added rate limits table for all 5 tiers\n- Added badge system (⚪🟢🔵🟣💎)\n- L1 docs now consistent with whitepaper and updated verification tiers","oldText":"## 7:45 AM (Heartbeat) — Free Explore Mode\n- Surfed Hacker News for interesting tech\n- **CanIRun.ai** — Tool to check which AI models your machine can run locally (825 pts)\n- **Qatar helium shutdown** — 30% global supply removed, chip supply chain on 2-week clock (357 pts)\n- **TUI Studio** — Visual editor for terminal UIs, exports to 6 frameworks (530 pts)\n- **Context Gateway** — Compresses agent context before hitting LLM, supports OpenClaw (55 pts)\n- **Algolia admin keys exposed** — 39 doc sites leaking admin keys (28 pts)"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":79400,"output":438,"cacheRead":3328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83166,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cache