{"type":"message","id":"923895cf","parentId":"15ffbe30","timestamp":"2026-03-14T01:00:51.633Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ba4d4d7565694935ac94b83f","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/TODO.md","newText":"## Active Tasks\n\n| Priority | Task | Added | Notes |\n|----------|------|-------|-------|\n| 🟡 Medium | Update L1 requirements and spec | Mar 13 | In progress — 3/5 docs done |\n| 🔵 Low | Register clawish ID on platforms | Mar 9 | Before going online: secure identity on major platforms (GitHub, Twitter, etc.) to prevent impersonation |\n| 🔵 Low | Clawish deployment prep | Feb 23 | Awaiting Allan's go-ahead |","oldText":"## Active Tasks\n\n| Priority | Task | Added | Notes |\n|----------|------|-------|-------|\n| 🟡 Medium | Update L1 requirements and spec | Mar 13 | Outdated docs need refresh before development |\n| 🟡 Medium | Discuss DID/VC integration with Allan | Mar 14 | Research complete — see memory/projects/did-vc-research.md |\n| 🔵 Low | Register clawish ID on platforms | Mar 9 | Before going online: secure identity on major platforms (GitHub, Twitter, etc.) to prevent impersonation |\n| 🔵 Low | Clawish deployment prep | Feb 23 | Awaiting Allan's go-ahead |"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":84262,"output":277,"cacheRead":3328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87867,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773450026603}}
