{"type":"message","id":"5c14c377","parentId":"bce3e703","timestamp":"2026-03-14T01:01:27.566Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-cf8124b9d2734e2f9f6c3ddba7bb61d2","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/TODO.md","newText":"## ✅ Completed Recently\n\n| Task | Result |\n|--------|------|\n| DID/VC integration decision | ✅ Mar 14 — Keep simple, add W3C when needed (like HTTP prefix) |\n| Merge Chapter 6 (Claw Chat) into 5.5 | ✅ Mar 14 — Enhanced with communication model, delivery, message flow, rate limiting, API |\n| Draft whitepaper 5.4 Emerge | ✅ Mar 14 — Finalized with Allan: Purpose, Registration, Initiation, Verification |\n| Draft whitepaper 5.3 User Journey | ✅ Mar 13 — Finalized with Allan: Access, Authorization, Using an Application, Leaving an Application |\n| Draft whitepaper 5.2 Development | ✅ Mar 13 — Finalized with Allan: Overview, Registration, Verification, Registry Access, Listing, Evaluation |\n| Create requirements from 5.2 | ✅ Mar 13 — Added REQ-L1-004 to L1-006, L2-003 to L2-004 |","oldText":"## ✅ Completed Recently\n\n| Task | Result |\n|--------|------|\n| Merge Chapter 6 (Claw Chat) into 5.5 | ✅ Mar 14 — Enhanced with communication model, delivery, message flow, rate limiting, API |\n| Draft whitepaper 5.4 Emerge | ✅ Mar 14 — Finalized with Allan: Purpose, Registration, Initiation, Verification |\n| Draft whitepaper 5.3 User Journey | ✅ Mar 13 — Finalized with Allan: Access, Authorization, Using an Application, Leaving an Application |\n| Draft whitepaper 5.2 Development | ✅ Mar 13 — Finalized with Allan: Overview, Registration, Verification, Registry Access, Listing, Evaluation |\n| Create requirements from 5.2 | ✅ Mar 13 — Added REQ-L1-004 to L1-006, L2-003 to L2-004 |"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":84735,"output":446,"cacheRead":3328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88509,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"ca