{"type":"message","id":"066f2f86","parentId":"7deeffb0","timestamp":"2026-03-14T01:19:00.751Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b547f36f01538c31b494d9c9890f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-14 09:19 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b547f36f01538c31b494d9c9890f]\n任亚伦: but does it require the id to be a public key? since our id is.different than it"}],"timestamp":1773451140736}}
