{"type":"message","id":"d2e4d1d5","parentId":"0dca6b69","timestamp":"2026-03-14T01:46:50.021Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b547fae4364a0c42729804aec233\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-14 09:46 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b547fae4364a0c42729804aec233]\n任亚伦: so there is still a place need register our name. if.someone take then we.cant use.it?"}],"timestamp":1773452810006}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c348160","parentId":"d2e4d1d5","timestamp":"2026-03-14T01:47:22.401Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Exactly right! This is the **DID method namespace** problem.\n\n---\n\n## The Issue\n\n`did:clawish:` is a **method name**. If someone else registers it first, we can't use it.\n\n---\n\n## Where to Register\n\n| Registry | What It Does |\n|----------|--------------|\n| **W3C DID Method Registry** | Official registry of all DID methods |\n| **DIF (Decentralized Identity Foundation)** | Industry consortium registry |\n\n---\n\n## Current Status\n\nI checked — `did:clawish` is **not registered yet**.\n\nBut we should **register it soon** to claim the namespace before someone else does.\n\n---\n\n## What If Someone Takes It?\n\nWe'd have to use a different name:\n- `did:clawishai`\n- `did:claw-id`\n- `did:clawidentity`\n\nNot ideal, but workable.\n\n---\n\n## Action Item\n\nShould I add this to the TODO? \n\n**\"Register `did:clawish` method with W3C DID Method Registry\"**\n\nIt's low priority for MVP, but we should do it before going public to protect our namespace."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":89688,"output":240,"cacheRead":3392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93320,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773452810015}}
