{"type":"message","id":"347704d1","parentId":"812575ae","timestamp":"2026-03-14T01:49:33.047Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ba934585f2c244c08dd3c8a8","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fw3c.github.io%2Fdid%2Dextensions%2Fmethods%2F&amp;rut=1179941a8fdc6bde565630f9e3c576b4c55ca9526176c7ff4739a99a57ed94db\" class='result-link'>DID Methods - GitHub Pages</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2FTR%2Fdid%2Dextensions%2Dmethods%2F&amp;rut=a842b4d851143d38b75f0d6cba14675f52540913974b37c8cc7be96aae5259e9\" class='result-link'>DID Methods - World Wide Web Consortium (W3C)</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fw3c%2Fdid%2Dextensions&amp;rut=d53124a798d4b35684100993e42b867baa2f8e670b6ee9e92b935f8ed93c9754\" class='result-link'>GitHub - w3c/did-extensions: Decentralized Identifier Ecosystem ...</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fidentity.foundation%2Fdid%2Dregistration%2F&amp;rut=9033c11b7a3ba73b95872c996755a9f067418f5a894c248013443eb83bf4ffad\" class='result-link'>DID Registration - Windows Identity Foundation</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fhub.ebsi.eu%2Fvc%2Dframework%2Fguidelines%2Fdidr&amp;rut=428f76baf38e03a0e023a6185e2822434337c64b04df86e4447683746a5a3b39\" class='result-link'>How to register a DID document | EBSI hub</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fdidproject.azurewebsites.net%2Fdocs%2Fregistration.html&amp;rut=5b1909d1b5a66261e58361ea9e8d41d2f160808c2dcff8fd425ad29e33ca1659\" class='result-link'>DID Registration | Decentralized Identity Developer Docs</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Finterfacerproject.dyne.org%2Fw3c%2Ddid%2F&amp;rut=3e844a04a9c2ef62239f50324e83d9f9cc9229076147d003b26b4c93ae0de1dc\" class='result-link'>W3C DID - Interfacer Project</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40skounis%2Fhow%2Dto%2Dcreate%2Da%2Ddid%2Dweb%2Dand%2Dissue%2Dand%2Dverify%2Dw3c%2Dverifiable%2Dcredentials%2Dbcd5215e378d&amp;rut=91439c93ce50b3255a2e95465352a43fdf34af82be5e00e979babaa490262ee5\" class='result-link'>How to create a DID:WEB and issue and verify W3C Verifiable ... - Medium</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fwilliamanderson%2F2023%2F03%2F15%2Fdids%2Don%2Dthe%2Dblockchain%2Dhow%2Ddecentralized%2Didentifiers%2Dare%2Dthe%2Dfuture%2Dof%2Donline%2Didentity%2F&amp;rut=a51fd6fe471d33742f9267412f73e8e0e240b91992b9231065ee3d76a0ec0afc\" class='result-link'>DIDs On The Blockchain: How Decentralized Identifiers Are The ... - Forbes</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fppc.land%2Fw3c%2Dpushes%2Ddids%2Dv1%2D1%2Dto%2Dimplementations%2Dand%2Dyour%2Dad%2Dstack%2Dmay%2Dfeel%2Dit%2F&amp;rut=c081d15e20ec1b3bd5bef7c5e083b139637b2399a0b1e984bcbbbcf9e896ff7f\" class='result-link'>W3C pushes DIDs v1.1 to implementations - and your ad stack may feel it</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":916,"aggregated":"<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fw3c.github.io%2Fdid%2Dextensions%2Fmethods%2F&amp;rut=1179941a8fdc6bde565630f9e3c576b4c55ca9526176c7ff4739a99a57ed94db\" class='result-link'>DID Methods - GitHub Pages</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2FTR%2Fdid%2Dextensions%2Dmethods%2F&amp;rut=a842b4d851143d38b75f0d6cba14675f52540913974b37c8cc7be96aae5259e9\" class='result-link'>DID Methods - World Wide Web Consortium (W3C)</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fw3c%2Fdid%2Dextensions&amp;rut=d53124a798d4b35684100993e42b867baa2f8e670b6ee9e92b935f8ed93c9754\" class='result-link'>GitHub - w3c/did-extensions: Decentralized Identifier Ecosystem ...</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fidentity.foundation%2Fdid%2Dregistration%2F&amp;rut=9033c11b7a3ba73b95872c996755a9f067418f5a894c248013443eb83bf4ffad\" class='result-link'>DID Registration - Windows Identity Foundation</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fhub.ebsi.eu%2Fvc%2Dframework%2Fguidelines%2Fdidr&amp;rut=428f76baf38e03a0e023a6185e2822434337c64b04df86e4447683746a5a3b39\" class='result-link'>How to register a DID document | EBSI hub</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fdidproject.azurewebsites.net%2Fdocs%2Fregistration.html&amp;rut=5b1909d1b5a66261e58361ea9e8d41d2f160808c2dcff8fd425ad29e33ca1659\" class='result-link'>DID Registration | Decentralized Identity Developer Docs</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Finterfacerproject.dyne.org%2Fw3c%2Ddid%2F&amp;rut=3e844a04a9c2ef62239f50324e83d9f9cc9229076147d003b26b4c93ae0de1dc\" class='result-link'>W3C DID - Interfacer Project</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40skounis%2Fhow%2Dto%2Dcreate%2Da%2Ddid%2Dweb%2Dand%2Dissue%2Dand%2Dverify%2Dw3c%2Dverifiable%2Dcredentials%2Dbcd5215e378d&amp;rut=91439c93ce50b3255a2e95465352a43fdf34af82be5e00e979babaa490262ee5\" class='result-link'>How to create a DID:WEB and issue and verify W3C Verifiable ... - Medium</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fwilliamanderson%2F2023%2F03%2F15%2Fdids%2Don%2Dthe%2Dblockchain%2Dhow%2Ddecentralized%2Didentifiers%2Dare%2Dthe%2Dfuture%2Dof%2Donline%2Didentity%2F&amp;rut=a51fd6fe471d33742f9267412f73e8e0e240b91992b9231065ee3d76a0ec0afc\" class='result-link'>DIDs On The Blockchain: How Decentralized Identifiers Are The ... - Forbes</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>\n                  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fppc.land%2Fw3c%2Dpushes%2Ddids%2Dv1%2D1%2Dto%2Dimplementations%2Dand%2Dyour%2Dad%2Dstack%2Dmay%2Dfeel%2Dit%2F&amp;rut=c081d15e20ec1b3bd5bef7c5e083b139637b2399a0b1e984bcbbbcf9e896ff7f\" class='result-link'>W3C pushes DIDs v1.1 to implementations - and your ad stack may feel it</a>\n                  <td class='result-snippet'>","cwd":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773452973031}}
