atforms\n- 🔵 Clawish deployment prep","oldText":"## 10:50 AM (Heartbeat)\n- No active conversation with Allan\n- L1 spec update: 4/5 docs done, remaining `01-overview.md`\n- Waiting for Allan's response or next task"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":92950,"output":587,"cacheRead":3392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96929,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773457517563}}
