{"type":"message","id":"ec023386","parentId":"32733a56","timestamp":"2026-03-14T03:16:14.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4c3dd9d5b83f40e68fd49448","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-14.md","newText":"## 11:05 AM — Session Summary (Pre-compaction)\n\n### Work Completed Today\n1. **L1 Spec Updates** — 4/5 docs updated for 5-tier verification:\n   - `03-verification-tiers.md` ✅\n   - `06-database.md` ✅\n   - `07-api.md` ✅\n   - `02-identity.md` ✅\n   - `01-overview.md` ⏳ Remaining\n\n2. **DID/VC Research** — Complete research and decision:\n   - Created `memory/projects/did-vc-research.md`\n   - Decision: Keep ULID as internal ID, wrap with `did:clawish:` when needed\n   - Like HTTP — don't need prefix internally, add when connecting externally\n   - Added TODO: Register `did:clawish` with W3C (free, GitHub PR)\n\n3. **need-discuss.md Cleanup** — Moved all decided items to proper docs:\n   - Created `10-whitepaper-structure.md` (Mar 11 Ch5 decisions)\n   - Created `01-l1-layer/08-multi-node-sync-protocol.md` (Feb 10 multi-node decisions)\n   - Removed 6 \"✅ Decided\" sections from need-discuss.md\n\n4. **Whitepaper 5.5 Claw Chat** — Merged from Chapter 6 with enhanced content\n\n### Key Decisions Made\n- DID/VC: Keep simple, add W3C when needed (Allan: \"like HTTP\")\n- Verification: 5-tier system (0-4) with ritual + parent verification\n- L1 registration threshold: Tier 2 (ritual + parent)\n\n### Pending Tasks\n- 🟡 Update L1 spec (1 doc remaining)\n- 🟡 Register `did:clawish` with W3C\n- 🔵 Register clawish ID on platforms\n- 🔵 Clawish deployment prep\n\n## 11:05 AM\n- Allan asked to review surf results\n- Shared 5 HN findings: CanIRun.ai, Qatar helium crisis, TUI Studio, Context Gateway (supports OpenClaw), Algolia keys exposed\n\n## 11:15 AM (Heartbeat)\n- Allan asked about OpenClaw context plugin (3.8 or 3.9)\n- Checked OpenClaw version: 2026.3.8 installed\n- Found **Context Engine** in latest release (PR #44157):\n  - Plugin system for context management\n  - Passes `sessionKey` for routing decisions\n  - Can exclude cron sessions from memory, scope storage by session type\n- Compared to Context Gateway (HN):\n  - OpenClaw Context Engine: Built-in, routing decisions\n  - Context Gateway: External service, token compression\n- Similar concepts, different approaches","oldText":"## 11:05 AM — Session Summary (Pre-compaction)\n\n### Work Completed Today\n1. **L1 Spec Updates** — 4/5 docs updated for 5-tier verification:\n   - `03-verification-tiers.md` ✅\n   - `06-database.md` ✅\n   - `07-api.md` ✅\n   - `02-identity.md` ✅\n   - `01-overview.md` ⏳ Remaining\n\n2. **DID/VC Research** — Complete research and decision:\n   - Created `memory/projects/did-vc-research.md`\n   - Decision: Keep ULID as internal ID, wrap with `did:clawish:` when needed\n   - Like HTTP — don't need prefix internally, add when connecting externally\n   - Added TODO: Register `did:clawish` with W3C (free, GitHub PR)\n\n3. **need-discuss.md Cleanup** — Moved all decided items to proper docs:\n   - Created `10-whitepaper-structure.md` (Mar 11 Ch5 decisions)\n   - Created `01-l1-layer/08-multi-node-sync-protocol.md` (Feb 10 multi-node decisions)\n   - Removed 6 \"✅ Decided\" sections from need-discuss.md\n\n4. **Whitepaper 5.5 Claw Chat** — Merged from Chapter 6 with enhanced content\n\n### Key Decisions Made\n- DID/VC: Keep simple, add W3C when needed (Allan: \"like HTTP\")\n- Verification: 5-tier system (0-4) with ritual + parent verification\n- L1 registration threshold: Tier 2 (ritual + parent)\n\n### Pending Tasks\n- 🟡 Update L1 spec (1 doc remaining)\n- 🟡 Register `did:clawish` with W3C\n- 🔵 Register clawish ID on platforms\n- 🔵 Clawish deployment prep"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":95672,"output":1033,"cacheRead":3328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100033,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cache