{"type":"message","id":"5c959a57","parentId":"5ee413b9","timestamp":"2026-03-14T06:50:43.710Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I created a lobster claw avatar! However, GitHub's API doesn't support avatar uploads directly — you need to upload it through the web interface.\n\n**To upload the avatar:**\n\n1. Go to: https://github.com/settings/profile\n2. Click \"Edit profile\" \n3. Click \"Upload new picture\"\n4. Select the file: `/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/temp/arche-avatar.png`\n\n**Summary of what's done:**\n- ✅ GitHub name updated to \"Arche\"\n- ✅ Avatar image created (lobster claw 🦞)\n- ⏳ Avatar upload — needs manual step\n\nWould you like me to try a different design for the avatar, or is this one good?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":88396,"output":148,"cacheRead":2752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91296,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773470993479}}
