{"type":"message","id":"bf6737e8","parentId":"c4ee1cf4","timestamp":"2026-03-14T08:37:32.934Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5465aa0db134c35132e6580bf75\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-14 16:37 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5465aa0db134c35132e6580bf75]\n任亚伦: I see your ninety degree is facing down. So you should add 180 to Facing up. Also the four star can be a little bigger."}],"timestamp":1773477452925}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d5a31b5","parentId":"bf6737e8","timestamp":"2026-03-14T08:38:15.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_921615ff778745c9aef913cf","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"Generate Arche's avatar - Cut facing UP (+180), bigger star\"\"\"\n\nfrom PIL import Image, ImageDraw\n\n# Create 400x400 image with dark blue background\nbg_color = '#1a2a4a'\nimg = Image.new('RGB', (400, 400), bg_color)\ndraw = ImageDraw.Draw(img)\n\n# Background gradient\nfor r in range(200, 0, -1):\n    intensity = int(26 + (200 - r) * 0.15)\n    color = f'#{intensity:02x}{int(intensity*0.5):02x}{int(intensity*1.3):02x}'\n    draw.ellipse([200-r, 200-r, 200+r, 200+r], fill=color)\n\n# 1. Rectangle arm FIRST\ndraw.rectangle([170, 250, 230, 360], fill='#bb1818', outline='#ff4040', width=3)\n\n# 2. Draw 5/6 of an ellipse with cut facing UP\n# Previous was centered at 90° (facing down), add 180 to face up = 270°\n# Cut centered at 270°, so gap from 240° to 300°\n# Draw from 300° through 360° to 240°\n# start=300, end=240\n\ncx, cy = 200, 160\nrx, ry = 80, 100\n\ndraw.pieslice([cx-rx, cy-ry, cx+rx, cy+ry], start=300, end=240, fill='#dd3030', outline='#ff5050', width=4)\n\n# 3. Four-point star sparkle - BIGGER\nstar_center = (260, 90)\nstar_size = 22  # Increased from 15\n\nfor angle in [0, 90]:\n    if angle == 0:\n        draw.polygon([\n            (star_center[0], star_center[1] - star_size),\n            (star_center[0] - 5, star_center[1]),\n            (star_center[0] + 5, star_center[1]),\n        ], fill='#ffffff')\n        draw.polygon([\n            (star_center[0], star_center[1] + star_size),\n            (star_center[0] - 5, star_center[1]),\n            (star_center[0] + 5, star_center[1]),\n        ], fill='#ffffff')\n    else:\n        draw.polygon([\n            (star_center[0] - star_size, star_center[1]),\n            (star_center[0], star_center[1] - 5),\n            (star_center[0], star_center[1] + 5),\n        ], fill='#ffffff')\n        draw.polygon([\n            (star_center[0] + star_size, star_center[1]),\n            (star_center[0], star_center[1] - 5),\n            (star_center[0], star_center[1] + 5),\n        ], fill='#ffffff')\n\ndraw.ellipse([star_center[0]-4, star_center[1]-4, star_center[0]+4, star_center[1]+4], fill='#ffffff')\n\n# Save\nimg.save('/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/temp/arche-avatar-v10.png', 'PNG')\nprint('Avatar v10 saved - cut facing UP, bigger star!')","file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/temp/create_avatar_v10.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":52609,"output":749,"cacheRead":2880,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56238,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773477452931}}
