{"type":"message","id":"d827f61a","parentId":"cd9be3b8","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:03:34.126Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Got it! Let me revise:\n\n---\n\n## Simplified Contacts Table\n\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE contacts (\n  peer_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,        -- e.g., 'ou_abc123...'\n  peer_name TEXT,                   -- e.g., 'Alice', 'Bob'\n  channel TEXT                      -- e.g., 'feishu', 'telegram'\n);\n```\n\n## Export Function\n\nExport conversations to markdown files, organized by peer and date:\n\n```\nexports/\n├── alice/\n│   └── 2026-03/\n│       ├── 2026-03-13.md\n│       └── 2026-03-14.md\n├── bob/\n│   └── 2026-03/\n│       └── 2026-03-12.md\n```\n\n### Export Format (same as our current chat logs)\n\n```markdown\n# 2026-03-14 — Alice\n\n## 2:30 PM\nAlice: Hello, how are you?\n\n## 2:31 PM\nArche: I'm doing well! Working on the LCM improvements.\n\n## 2:35 PM\nAlice: That sounds interesting!\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Features to Add\n\n| Feature | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Contacts table** | `peer_id`, `peer_name`, `channel` |\n| **Peer columns in conversations** | Link conversations to contacts |\n| **Peer extraction** | Parse messages to extract peer info |\n| **Export function** | Export to MD files by peer/date |\n\n---\n\nShould I start implementing this?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":78760,"output":329,"cacheRead":2752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81841,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773493365748}}
