{"type":"message","id":"e8da0455","parentId":"cddd69cd","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:04:57.764Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good point! Let me update the export structure:\n\n---\n\n## Export Structure (with DM/Group separation)\n\n```\nexports/\n├── dm/\n│   ├── alice/\n│   │   └── 2026-03/\n│   │       ├── 2026-03-13.md\n│   │       └── 2026-03-14.md\n│   └── bob/\n│       └── 2026-03/\n│           └── 2026-03-12.md\n└── group/\n    ├── project-alpha/\n    │   └── 2026-03/\n    │       └── 2026-03-14.md\n    └── team-meeting/\n        └── 2026-03/\n            └── 2026-03-10.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## Updated Schema\n\n```sql\n-- Contacts table\nCREATE TABLE contacts (\n  peer_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  peer_name TEXT,\n  channel TEXT\n);\n\n-- Add to conversations table\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN peer_id TEXT;\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN chat_type TEXT;  -- 'dm' or 'group'\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Feature | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Contacts table** | `peer_id`, `peer_name`, `channel` |\n| **Chat type** | Separate DM vs Group |\n| **Export** | `dm/{peer}/YYYY-MM/YYYY-MM-DD.md` or `group/{name}/YYYY-MM/YYYY-MM-DD.md` |\n\nReady to implement?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":79321,"output":327,"cacheRead":2752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82400,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773493459108}}
