{"type":"message","id":"473326b9","parentId":"48e00765","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:13:53.793Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## LCM Enhancement: Changes Summary\n\n### 1. Database Schema Changes\n\n**New table: `contacts`**\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE contacts (\n  peer_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  peer_name TEXT,\n  channel TEXT\n);\n```\n\n**Add columns to `conversations` table**\n```sql\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN peer_id TEXT;\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN chat_type TEXT;  -- 'dm' or 'group'\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. Peer Extraction Logic\n\nExtract peer info from message content using regex patterns:\n- Feishu DM format\n- Telegram format\n- Generic inbound metadata JSON\n\nAuto-populate `contacts` table when new peer detected.\n\n---\n\n### 3. Export Function\n\nExport conversations to markdown files:\n\n```\nexports/\n├── dm/\n│   └── {peer_name}/\n│       └── {YYYY-MM}/\n│           └── {YYYY-MM-DD}.md\n└── group/\n    └── {group_name}/\n        └── {YYYY-MM}/\n            └── {YYYY-MM-DD}.md\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. Enhanced Search\n\nAdd peer filtering to `lcm_grep`:\n- `--peer <name>` — filter by peer name\n- `--channel <channel>` — filter by channel\n- `--chat-type <dm|group>` — filter by chat type\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Order\n\n| Step | Task |\n|------|------|\n| 1 | Fork LCM repo |\n| 2 | Add `contacts` table to schema |\n| 3 | Add `peer_id`, `chat_type` to `conversations` |\n| 4 | Add peer extraction logic |\n| 5 | Add export function |\n| 6 | Update search tools |\n| 7 | Test locally |\n| 8 | (Optional) Submit PR upstream |\n\n---\n\nReady to start?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":80392,"output":396,"cacheRead":2752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83540,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773493982590}}
