{"type":"message","id":"8dc2836f","parentId":"cc188078","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:25:23.719Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good point! Let me add that to the plan:\n\n---\n\n## LCM Enhancement: Updated Changes Summary\n\n### 1. Database Schema Changes\n\n**New table: `contacts`**\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE contacts (\n  peer_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  peer_name TEXT,\n  channel TEXT\n);\n```\n\n**Add columns to `conversations` table**\n```sql\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN peer_id TEXT;\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN chat_type TEXT;  -- 'dm' or 'group'\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. Peer Extraction Logic\n\nExtract peer info from message content using regex patterns.\n\n---\n\n### 3. CLI Export Command\n\nAdd new CLI option:\n\n```bash\nlcm export --output ./exports\nlcm export --peer alice --output ./exports\nlcm export --chat-type dm --output ./exports\nlcm export --from 2026-03-01 --to 2026-03-14 --output ./exports\n```\n\n**Export structure:**\n```\nexports/\n├── dm/\n│   └── {peer_name}/\n│       └── {YYYY-MM}/\n│           └── {YYYY-MM-DD}.md\n└── group/\n    └── {group_name}/\n        └── {YYYY-MM}/\n            └── {YYYY-MM-DD}.md\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. Enhanced Search\n\nAdd peer filtering to `lcm_grep`:\n- `--peer <name>` — filter by peer name\n- `--channel <channel>` — filter by channel\n- `--chat-type <dm|group>` — filter by chat type\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Order\n\n| Step | Task |\n|------|------|\n| 1 | Fork LCM repo |\n| 2 | Add `contacts` table to schema |\n| 3 | Add `peer_id`, `chat_type` to `conversations` |\n| 4 | Add peer extraction logic |\n| 5 | Add CLI `export` command |\n| 6 | Update search tools |\n| 7 | Test locally |\n| 8 | (Optional) Submit PR upstream |\n\n---\n\nReady to start?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":81521,"output":449,"cacheRead":2752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84722,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773494675542}}
