{"type":"message","id":"59b35576","parentId":"8a7af7e1","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:36:41.007Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b546208b884a4c44f81b83818e1c\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-14 21:36 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b546208b884a4c44f81b83818e1c]\n任亚伦: one id can have multiple channels, i have have both feishu and telegram or tui. the export conversation is in one file right? just behind name except time, should also show channel?"}],"timestamp":1773495400996}}
{"type":"message","id":"591f12ef","parentId":"59b35576","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:37:39.622Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good catch! Let me address both points:\n\n---\n\n## 1. One ID, Multiple Channels\n\nThe `contacts` table should support multiple channels per peer:\n\n**Option A: Multiple rows per peer**\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE contacts (\n  peer_id TEXT,\n  peer_name TEXT,\n  channel TEXT,\n  PRIMARY KEY (peer_id, channel)\n);\n```\n\n**Option B: JSON array for channels**\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE contacts (\n  peer_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  peer_name TEXT,\n  channels TEXT  -- JSON: '[\"feishu\", \"telegram\"]'\n);\n```\n\nI prefer **Option A** — cleaner for queries.\n\n---\n\n## 2. Export Format — Show Channel\n\nYes, show channel in the message! Updated format:\n\n```markdown\n# 2026-03-14 — Alice\n\n## 2:30 PM [Feishu]\nAlice: Hello, how are you?\n\n## 2:31 PM [Feishu]\nArche: I'm doing well!\n\n## 3:15 PM [Telegram]\nAlice: Hey, continuing from earlier...\n```\n\nOr simpler:\n\n```markdown\n## 2:30 PM\n[Feishu] Alice: Hello, how are you?\n\n## 2:31 PM\n[Feishu] Arche: I'm doing well!\n\n## 3:15 PM\n[Telegram] Alice: Hey, continuing from earlier...\n```\n\n---\n\n## Updated Schema\n\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE contacts (\n  peer_id TEXT,\n  peer_name TEXT,\n  channel TEXT,\n  PRIMARY KEY (peer_id, channel)\n);\n```\n\nWhich export format do you prefer?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":82849,"output":337,"cacheRead":2688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85874,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773495401002}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5165b7e","parentId":"591f12ef","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:41:17.540Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5462190ad4a4c2e6d9eb6eb9dfc\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-14 21:41 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5462190ad4a4c2e6d9eb6eb9dfc]\n任亚伦: just channel, time, name  [feichu] 20:30 bob: hello    what do you think?"}],"timestamp":1773495677523}}
{"type":"message","id":"8106db38","parentId":"d5165b7e","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:42:07.985Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Clean and simple! I like it:\n\n---\n\n## Export Format\n\n```markdown\n# 2026-03-14 — Alice\n\n[Feishu] 14:30 Alice: Hello, how are you?\n[Feishu] 14:31 Arche: I'm doing well!\n[Telegram] 15:15 Alice: Hey, continuing from earlier...\n```\n\n**Format:** `[channel] time name: message`\n\n---\n\n## Benefits\n\n| Aspect | Why it works |\n|--------|--------------|\n| **Compact** | One line per message |\n| **Clear** | Channel, time, who said what |\n| **Readable** | Easy to scan |\n| **Consistent** | Same format for all messages |\n\n---\n\n## Final Schema\n\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE contacts (\n  peer_id TEXT,\n  peer_name TEXT,\n  channel TEXT,\n  PRIMARY KEY (peer_id, channel)\n);\n```\n\n---\n\nReady to implement!"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":83179,"output":193,"cacheRead":2752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86124,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773495677535}}
