{"type":"message","id":"f03a7c23","parentId":"6e61c679","timestamp":"2026-03-14T14:04:35.335Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Exactly! So the final schema is:\n\n---\n\n## Final LCM Schema\n\n### `contacts` table\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE contacts (\n  peer_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  peer_name TEXT,\n  chat_type TEXT  -- 'dm' or 'group'\n);\n```\n\n### `conversations` table (add columns)\n```sql\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN peer_id TEXT;\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN channel TEXT;\n```\n\n---\n\n## Export Structure\n\n```\nexports/\n├── dm/\n│   └── alice/\n│       └── 2026-03/\n│           └── 2026-03-14.md\n└── group/\n    └── project-alpha/\n        └── 2026-03/\n            └── 2026-03-14.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Table | Purpose |\n|-------|---------|\n| **contacts** | Map peer_id → peer_name + chat_type (dm/group) |\n| **conversations** | Add peer_id + channel |\n\nThis way:\n- `chat_type` determines folder (`dm/` or `group/`)\n- `peer_name` determines subfolder\n- `channel` shows in message line\n\nReady to implement tomorrow! 🦞💤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":83012,"output":263,"cacheRead":5888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89163,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773497025934}}
{"type":"message","id":"f3527cfc","parentId":"f03a7c23","timestamp":"2026-03-14T14:04:36.515Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Exactly! So the final schema is:\n\n---\n\n## Final LCM Schema\n\n### `contacts` table\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE contacts (\n  peer_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  peer_name TEXT,\n  chat_type TEXT  -- 'dm' or 'group'\n);\n```\n\n### `conversations` table (add columns)\n```sql\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN peer_id TEXT;\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN channel TEXT;\n```\n\n---\n\n## Export Structure\n\n```\nexports/\n├── dm/\n│   └── alice/\n│       └── 2026-03/\n│           └── 2026-03-14.md\n└── group/\n    └── project-alpha/\n        └── 2026-03/\n            └── 2026-03-14.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Table | Purpose |\n|-------|---------|\n| **contacts** | Map peer_id → peer_name + chat_type (dm/group) |\n| **conversations** | Add peer_id + channel |\n\nThis way:\n- `chat_type` determines folder (`dm/` or `group/`)\n- `peer_name` determines subfolder\n- `channel` shows in message line\n\nReady to implement tomorrow! 🦞💤"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773497076515}}
