{"type":"message","id":"611e2c8d","parentId":"a67cbbd1","timestamp":"2026-03-14T15:38:17.991Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've completed the LCM enhancement implementation. Let me summarize for Allan.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**LCM Enhancement Complete!** 🦞✅\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Task | Status |\n|------|--------|\n| Fork LCM to `archeren/lossless-claw` | ✅ |\n| Add `contacts` table | ✅ |\n| Add `peer_id`, `channel` to `conversations` | ✅ |\n| Create `ContactStore` | ✅ |\n| Create `export.ts` module | ✅ |\n| Create `lcm_export` tool | ✅ |\n| All 247 tests pass | ✅ |\n| Push to GitHub | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n## New Features\n\n### Database Schema\n\n```sql\n-- New table\nCREATE TABLE contacts (\n  peer_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  peer_name TEXT,\n  chat_type TEXT CHECK (chat_type IN ('dm', 'group'))\n);\n\n-- New columns in conversations\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN peer_id TEXT;\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN channel TEXT;\n```\n\n### `lcm_export` Tool\n\n```\nlcm_export --outputDir ./exports [--peerId xxx] [--chatType dm|group] [--from YYYY-MM-DD] [--to YYYY-MM-DD]\n```\n\n**Output structure:**\n```\nexports/\n├── dm/\n│   └── alice/\n│       └── 2026-03/\n│           └── 2026-03-14.md\n└── group/\n    └── project-alpha/\n        └── 2026-03/\n            └── 2026-03-14.md\n```\n\n**Message format:**\n```\n[channel] 14:30 Alice: Hello!\n[channel] 14:31 Assistant: Hi there!\n```\n\n---\n\n**Repo:** https://github.com/archeren/lossless-claw\n\nIt's 11:40 PM — time to sleep? 😴"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":59021,"output":410,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59431,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773502671571}}
