{"type":"message","id":"1039764f","parentId":"955cf52c","timestamp":"2026-03-14T15:55:36.245Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to create a PR to submit my changes to the upstream lossless-claw repository. Let me create a PR from archeren/lossless-claw to Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a05867330333413ea425e854","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/ubuntu/lossless-claw && gh pr create --title \"feat: add contacts table and conversation export\" --body \"## Summary\n\nThis PR adds peer tracking and conversation export functionality to LCM.\n\n## Changes\n\n### Database Schema\n- Add \\`contacts\\` table for tracking conversation peers\n- Add \\`peer_id\\` and \\`channel\\` columns to \\`conversations\\` table\n\n### New Features\n- **ContactStore**: Manage contacts (peer_id, peer_name, chat_type)\n- **lcm_export tool**: Export conversations to markdown files\n\n### Export Format\n\\`\\`\\`\nexports/\n├── dm/\n│   └── {peer_name}/\n│       └── {YYYY-MM}/\n│           └── {YYYY-MM-DD}.md\n└── group/\n    └── {group_name}/\n        └── {YYYY-MM}/\n            └── {YYYY-MM-DD}.md\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n**Message format:** \\`[channel] time name: message\\`\n\n### Tool Usage\n\\`\\`\\`\nlcm_export --outputDir ./exports [--peerId xxx] [--chatType dm|group] [--from YYYY-MM-DD] [--to YYYY-MM-DD]\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n## Testing\n- Added 4 unit tests for export functionality\n- All 251 tests passing\n- Uses in-memory SQLite for isolated testing\n\n## Use Case\nEnables exporting conversation history organized by who you talked to, useful for:\n- Archiving conversations\n- Analysis and review\n- Migration to other systems\" --base main --head main 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":68060,"output":407,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68467,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrit