{"type":"message","id":"405bec51","parentId":"cebbc974","timestamp":"2026-03-14T16:54:17.317Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OpenClaw plugins can register hooks via `api.registerHook()`. I found:\n- `message_received` hook - triggered when a message is received\n- `registerHook` is available in the plugin API\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Add a `message_received` hook to the LCM plugin\n2. Extract peer info from the message metadata\n3. Call `updateConversationPeer` with the extracted info\n\nLet me update the LCM plugin to add this hook.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Found it! OpenClaw has a `message_received` hook. Let me add it to LCM:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e883fbb36cd945919a6cda08","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/lossless-claw/index.ts","limit":80,"offset":1310}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":100486,"output":193,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100679,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773507214923}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ccd366d","parentId":"405bec51","timestamp":"2026-03-14T16:54:17.348Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e883fbb36cd945919a6cda08","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"      }),\n    );\n    api.registerTool((ctx) =>\n      createLcmExpandQueryTool({\n        deps,\n        lcm,\n        sessionKey: ctx.sessionKey,\n        requesterSessionKey: ctx.sessionKey,\n      }),\n    );\n    api.registerTool((ctx) =>\n      createLcmExportTool({\n        deps,\n      }),\n    );\n    api.registerTool((ctx) =>\n      createLcmUpdatePeerTool({\n        deps,\n        lcm,\n        sessionId: ctx.sessionId,\n        sessionKey: ctx.sessionKey,\n      }),\n    );\n\n    api.logger.info(\n      `[lcm] Plugin loaded (enabled=${deps.config.enabled}, db=${deps.config.databasePath}, threshold=${deps.config.contextThreshold})`,\n    );\n  },\n};\n\nexport default lcmPlugin;\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773507257328}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ea14dec","parentId":"8ccd366d","timestamp":"2026-03-14T16:55:06.846Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to add a `message_received` hook to the LCM plugin. The hook should:\n1. Receive the message event\n2. Extract peer info (sender_id, sender_name, channel, chat_type)\n3. Call `lcm.updateConversationPeer()` with the extracted info\n\nLet me add this hook to the plugin registration.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0a13aad58ff3435888093c1b","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/lossless-claw/index.ts","newText":"    api.registerTool((ctx) =>\n      createLcmUpdatePeerTool({\n        deps,\n        lcm,\n        sessionId: ctx.sessionId,\n        sessionKey: ctx.sessionKey,\n      }),\n    );\n\n    // Register hook to auto-extract peer info from inbound messages\n    api.registerHook([\"message_received\"], async (event) => {\n      const meta = event.context?.inboundMeta;\n      if (!meta) return;\n\n      const sessionId = event.sessionId;\n      if (!sessionId) return;\n\n      // Extract peer info from inbound metadata\n      const chatId = meta.chat_id;\n      const channel = meta.channel;\n      const chatType = meta.chat_type;\n\n      // For DMs, the peer is the sender\n      // For groups, the peer is the chat/group\n      let peerId: string | undefined;\n      let peerName: string | undefined;\n\n      if (chatType === \"dm\" && meta.sender_id) {\n        peerId = `user:${meta.sender_id}`;\n        peerName = meta.sender_name || meta.sender;\n      } else if (chatType === \"group\" && chatId) {\n        peerId = chatId;\n        peerName = meta.chat_name || meta.group_name;\n      }\n\n      if (!peerId) return;\n\n      // Update conversation with peer info\n      try {\n        await lcm.updateConversationPeer({\n          sessionId,\n          peerId,\n          peerName,\n          channel,\n          chatType,\n        });\n        deps.log.info(`[lcm] Auto-extracted peer: ${peerId} (${peerName || \"unknown\"}) for session ${sessionId}`);\n      } catch (error) {\n        deps.log.warn(`[lcm] Failed to update peer info: ${error}`);\n      }\n    });\n\n    api.logger.info(","oldText":"    api.registerTool((ctx) =>\n      createLcmUpdatePeerTool({\n        deps,\n        lcm,\n        sessionId: ctx.sessionId,\n        sessionKey: ctx.sessionKey,\n      }),\n    );\n\n    api.logger.info("}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":100797,"output":540,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101337,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773507257344}}
