om/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pulls/64\"},\"html\":{\"href\":\"https://github.com/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pull/64\"},\"issue\":{\"href\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/issues/64\"},\"comments\":{\"href\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/issues/64/comments\"},\"review_comments\":{\"href\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pulls/64/comments\"},\"review_comment\":{\"href\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pulls/comments{/number}\"},\"commits\":{\"href\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pulls/64/commits\"},\"statuses\":{\"href\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/statuses/cfdfdbc267614bebadcbff25618509e2449fb8e1\"}},\"author_association\":\"NONE\",\"auto_merge\":null,\"assignee\":null,\"active_lock_reason\":null,\"merged\":false,\"mergeable\":true,\"rebaseable\":true,\"mergeable_state\":\"clean\",\"merged_by\":null,\"comments\":0,\"review_comments\":0,\"maintainer_can_modify\":true,\"commits\":6,\"additions\":913,\"deletions\":25,\"changed_files\":13}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":766,"aggregated":"{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pulls/64\",\"id\":3399332335,\"node_id\":\"PR_kwDORTexc87KnbHv\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pull/64\",\"diff_url\":\"https://github.com/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pull/64.diff\",\"patch_url\":\"https://github.com/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pull/64.patch\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/issues/64\",\"number\":64,\"state\":\"open\",\"locked\":false,\"title\":\"feat: add contacts table and conversation export\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"archeren\",\"id\":258648223,\"node_id\":\"U_kgDOD2qonw\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/258648223?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/archeren\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"body\":\"## Summary\\n\\nThis PR adds peer tracking and conversation export functionality to LCM, enabling organized export of conversations by who you talked to.\\n\\n## Features\\n\\n### 1. Database Schema\\n\\n**New `contacts` table:**\\n```sql\\nCREATE TABLE contacts (\\n  peer_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\\n  peer_name TEXT,\\n  chat_type TEXT CHECK (chat_type IN ('dm', 'group'))\\n);\\n```\\n\\n**New columns in `conversations` table:**\\n```sql\\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN peer_id TEXT REFERENCES contacts(peer_id);\\nALTER TABLE conversations ADD COLUMN channel TEXT;\\n```\\n\\n### 2. ContactStore\\n\\nNew store for managing contacts:\\n- `create()` — Create or update a contact\\n- `get()` — Get contact by peer_id\\n- `getAll()` — List all contacts\\n- `update()` — Update contact fields\\n- `delete()` — Delete a contact\\n\\n### 3. lcm_export Tool\\n\\nExport conversations to markdown files organized by peer and date.\\n\\n```bash\\nlcm_export --outputDir ./exports\\nlcm_export --peerId \\\"user:ou_xxx\\\"\\nlcm_export --chatType dm\\nlcm_export --from 2026-03-01 --to 2026-03-15\\n```\\n\\n**Output structure:**\\n```\\nexports/\\n├── dm/\\n│   └── Alice/\\n│       └── 2026-03/\\n│           └── 2026-03-14.md\\n└── group/\\n    └── Project-Alpha/\\n        └── 2026-03/\\n            └── 2026-03-14.md\\n```\\n\\n**Message format:**\\n```\\n[channel] 14:30 Alice: Hello, how are you?\\n[channel] 14:31 Assistant: I'm doing well, thanks!\\n```\\n\\n### 4. Enhanced lcm_grep\\n\\nAdded peer filters to conversation search:\\n\\n```bash\\nlcm_grep --pattern \\\"hello\\\" --peerId \\\"user:ou_xxx\\\"\\nlcm_grep --pattern \\\"meeting\\\" --chatType group\\nlcm_grep --pattern \\\"bug\\\" --channel feishu\\n```\\n\\n### 5. Automatic Peer Extraction\\n\\nRegistered `message_received` hook to auto-extract peer info from inbound messages:\\n\\n- **DMs**: peer = sender (`user:xxx`)\\n- **Groups**: peer = chat/group (`chat:xxx`)\\n\\nNo manual setup required — contacts are created automatically when messages arrive.\\n\\n### 6. lcm_update_peer Tool (Manual Override)\\n\\nManually update peer info if needed:\\n\\n```bash\\nlcm_update_peer --peerId \\\"user:ou_xxx\\\" --peerName \\\"Alice\\\" --channel feishu --chatType dm\\n```\\n\\n## Testing\\n\\n- Added 4 unit tests for export functionality\\n- All 251 tests passing\\n- Uses in-memory SQLite for isolated testing\\n\\n## Use Cases\\n\\n- **Archive conversations** organized by who you talked to\\n- **Search history** filtered by peer, channel, or chat type\\n- **Export for analysis** or migration to other systems\\n- **Audit trails** with clear organization by contact\\n\\n## Breaking Changes\\n\\nNone. The schema additions are additive and backward-compatible.\\n\\n## Migration\\n\\nExisting LCM databases will be automatically migrated on next startup with the new columns and contacts table.\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-14T15:56:14Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-14T17:05:14Z\",\"closed_at\":null,\"merged_at\":null,\"merge_commit_sha\":\"06b20b459a6a3efe178dc7deb2a9f4b7c8d7e950\",\"assignees\":[],\"requested_reviewers\":[],\"requested_teams\":[],\"labels\":[],\"milestone\":null,\"draft\":false,\"commits_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pulls/64/commits\",\"review_comments_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pulls/64/comments\",\"review_comment_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pulls/comments{/number}\",\"comments_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/issues/64/comments\",\"statuses_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/statuses/cfdfdbc267614bebadcbff25618509e2449fb8e1\",\"head\":{\"label\":\"archeren:main\",\"ref\":\"main\",\"sha\":\"cfdfdbc267614bebadcbff25618509e2449fb8e1\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"archeren\",\"id\":258648223,\"node_id\":\"U_kgDOD2qonw\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/258648223?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/archeren\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/archeren/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"repo\":{\"id\":1181713894,\"node_id\":\"R_kgDORm-F5g\",\"name\":\"lossless-claw\",\"full_name\":\"archeren/lossless-claw\",\"private\":false,\"owner\":{\"login\":\"archeren\",\"id\":258648223,\"node_id\":\"U_kgDOD2qonw\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/25